    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 146</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> faint evocation <strong>CL</strong> 5th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> weapon quality; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>This special ability can only be placed on melee weapons. An <em>ominous </em>weapon trails a shadowy haze behind every stroke, and moans a menacing dirge in battle. An <em>ominous</em> weapon adds its enhancement bonus on Intimidate checks made by the wielder. In addition, when an <em>ominous </em>weapon confirms a critical hit, the target is shaken for 1 minute (DC 13 Will negates); if the weapon's critical multiplier is greater than x2, this condition lasts 1 additional minute per multiple over x2. A creature that gains the shaken condition from an <em>ominous </em>weapon cannot gain that condition again from the same weapon for 24 hours.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>doom </em>or <em>scare</em>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
